  <p class="mb-4">
    All funded accounts — Growth, Lightning, Select Flex, and Select Daily — are <strong>simulated funded accounts</strong>. <strong>Tradeify Elite Live</strong> is the real-capital live stage, issued through NinjaTrader brokerage.
