      <p>Account sizes from $50K to $150K with monthly fees starting at $139, no activation fee. End-of-day trailing drawdown based on balance, not equity.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-teal-600 font-semibold mt-1">EOD trailing drawdown gives more room during live sessions</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Lightning Funded – Instant Funding</p>
      <p>Account sizes from $25K to $150K with one-time fees from $349. Skip the evaluation and start trading immediately in a simulated funded environment.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-teal-600 font-semibold mt-1">Best for experienced traders who want immediate access without evaluation</p>
