    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-100 border border-slate-300 p-4 opacity-70">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-600 mb-1">Advanced Challenge – Legacy Only <span class="text-xs bg-slate-200 text-slate-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full ml-1">No Longer Available</span></p>
