      The Growth Challenge is Tradeify's 1-step evaluation with <strong>no activation fee</strong> and monthly fees from $139 to $339 depending on account size.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-3">
      This model uses <strong>end-of-day trailing drawdown</strong>, calculated only after markets close and only if your balance increases. That means you can ride through intraday drawdowns without triggering a loss, as long as your closed trades stay clean.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      The minimum trading period is just one day to pass the evaluation. The reset fee is $85. For funded payouts, traders need <strong>5 profitable trading days</strong> meeting the per-account profit threshold.
    </p>

